    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-cc72c9d3-7fff-92fb-1cc4-9a5b3877577b\">You were always interested in the healing properties of fluids. In your experiments you managed to replicate the effects of proper Alchemical and Magical Healing without using Standard variants. You can craft Healing Potions and Elixirs of Life up to your Level, even if you don’t possess the Alchemical Crafting or Magical Crafting feats. You still need to fulfill the other requirements to craft the Consumables.</span></p>",
